##Fees
VirWoX charges 50 SLL (currently about 0.02 BTC) plus 1% for BTC/SLL market orders. The fee for limit orders depends on the previous trading volume of the account, and varies between 0.78% and 3.9% (9.1).

VirWoX charges 0.02 BTC for BTC withdrawals. Deposits in BTC are free.

##Limits and Restrictions

Because of the risks involved, VirWoX restricts deposits via PayPal and Moneybookers (i.e. Credit/Debit Cards) depending on the age of the account. Initially you can deposit only 60 EUR (or 84 USD) per day. This limit grows to 500 EUR or 700 USD per day after 30 days (10.1). Higher limits are available on request.

Another quite serious restriction is that trades are limited to whole units. E.g. you can only trade whole EUR to Linden Dollars (SLL). Even bigger is the problem that you can only buy whole bitcoins. Since one bitcoin is now worth a 4-digit amount of SLL this is a really big restriction - you'll quite probably end up with a bigger rest of SLL and have to spend additional money to use this rest.

